  "description": "NAT Gateway egress bytes per NAT GW. Watch during the IPv6 cutover soak window — pod-to-IPv4-internet egress (image pulls from ghcr.io / nvcr.io / public.ecr.aws and any IPv6-less destination) routes through the IPv4 NAT GW. Spike > 2x pre-cutover baseline indicates an unexpected IPv4-only destination set; investigate via VPC flow logs. TODO(observability-gap): NAT GW metrics come from CloudWatch (`AWS/NATGateway` namespace, e.g. `BytesOutToDestination`). OSDC's monitoring stack does not yet ship a CloudWatch exporter (e.g. `cloudwatch-exporter` / YACE). Until one is wired up, the panels below render no data — the dashboard is staged so panels light up automatically once the exporter lands.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": true,
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": true,
      "keepTime": true,
      "tags": ["osdc"],
      "targetBlank": true,
      "title": "OSDC Dashboards",
      "type": "dashboards"
    }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Observability gap (read first)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "code": {"language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false},
        "content": "**This dashboard renders no data until a CloudWatch exporter is deployed.**\n\nNAT Gateway metrics live in CloudWatch (`AWS/NATGateway` namespace), not in Mimir. OSDC's monitoring stack does not yet ship `cloudwatch-exporter` or YACE. The panels below reference `aws_natgateway_bytes_out_to_destination` (the canonical Prometheus name produced by `prometheus/cloudwatch_exporter`) — once the exporter is wired up, this dashboard activates automatically.\n\n**Until then**, watch NAT GW egress directly in the AWS console: `CloudWatch → Metrics → AWS/NATGateway → NatGatewayId, Per-NAT GW`. The IPv6 cutover runbook (`docs/ipv6-cluster-recreation.md`) documents the > 2x baseline threshold under \"Soak window\"."
      }
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5},
      "id": 2,
      "title": "NAT Gateway Egress (per NAT GW)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "description": "Bytes out to destination per NAT GW. Sum across all NAT GWs in the cluster's VPC. Spike > 2x baseline during the IPv6 soak window means IPv6 pods are hitting unexpected IPv4-only destinations — investigate via VPC flow logs.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "none"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "Bps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6},
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
          "expr": "rate(aws_natgateway_bytes_out_to_destination_sum{cluster=\"$cluster\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{nat_gateway_id}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "NAT GW Bytes Out To Destination (per NAT GW, rate over 5m)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "description": "Total bytes out across all NAT GWs in the cluster's VPC, summed. Baseline this against pre-cutover IPv4 numbers; sustained > 2x is the alert threshold per docs/ipv6-cluster-recreation.md.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "none"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "Bps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14},
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
          "expr": "sum(rate(aws_natgateway_bytes_out_to_destination_sum{cluster=\"$cluster\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Total NAT GW egress",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "NAT GW Total Bytes Out (cluster-wide, rate over 5m)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "description": "Active connections per NAT GW. Pairs with conntrack-table-fill alerts on the node side — NAT GW connection count tracks pod-to-IPv4-internet flow count.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "none"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14},
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
          "expr": "aws_natgateway_active_connection_count_average{cluster=\"$cluster\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{nat_gateway_id}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "NAT GW Active Connections (per NAT GW)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22},
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Per-Node Conntrack Pressure (cross-reference)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
      "description": "Per-node conntrack table fill ratio. Top consumers indicate nodes most at risk of `nf_conntrack: table full, dropping packet`. Powered by the `network-pressure-alerts` PrometheusRule (NodeConntrackHighWarn at 0.80, NodeConntrackHighCritical at 0.95).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "none"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "line"}
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.80},
              {"color": "red", "value": 0.95}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 23},
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}"},
          "expr": "topk(20, node_nf_conntrack_entries{cluster=\"$cluster\"} / node_nf_conntrack_entries_limit{cluster=\"$cluster\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{instance}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Top 20 Nodes by Conntrack Table Fill",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "1m",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
